Shawn,

i'm with Jason on this one. check ALL of your other front end
components before even going near that steering box.

-ball joints
-steering damper
-correct tires?
-steering linkage
-wheel bearings

my old 74 Westy also had this problem & it turned out to be
bad ball joints.

